<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset='utf-8' />
    <title>Reply to User</title>
    <style>
      body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; } h1 { color: #333; } p {
      margin-bottom: 10px; } blockquote { margin: 10px 0; padding: 10px;
      border-left: 4px solid #ccc; background-color: #f9f9f9; } .footer {
      margin-top: 30px; color: #777; font-size: 12px; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Reply to Your Inquiry: {{supportMessage}}</h1>

    <p>Dear {{name}},</p>

    <p>Thank you for reaching out to us. We have received your message and would
      like to provide a response:</p>

    <blockquote>{{replyMessage}}</blockquote>

    <p>If you have any further questions or concerns, please feel free to reply
      to this email. We are here to assist you.</p>

    <div class='footer'>
      <p>Best regards,</p>
      <p>{{appName}} Team</p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>